component_description: Detection results for Header / User Profile Section

elements.label: Header / User Profile Section > Profile Image
elements.description: Small circular profile picture in the top-left portion of the screen, showing an image with a bluish background.
elements.explanation: The bounding box tightly surrounds the circular profile image with minor excess padding on the left. Well-positioned and proportionate, very accurate.

elements.label: Header / User Profile Section > Welcome Text
elements.description: Light gray text reading 'Welcome,' positioned to the right of the profile image at the top of the screen.
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the location and size of the 'Welcome,' text string. Accurate height and width, with very slight overhang.

elements.label: Header / User Profile Section > User Name
elements.description: Bold dark text 'Diane Cruz' displayed directly below the welcome text in the top section of the screen.
elements.explanation: Bounding box precisely encloses the user name text. Nearly perfect alignment.

elements.label: Header / User Profile Section > Notification Bell
elements.description: Bell-shaped icon positioned in the top-right corner of the screen, featuring a small teal dot indicator.
elements.explanation: Bounding box accurately encompasses the bell icon and its teal indicator, with a slight surplus on the right edge.

elements.label: Header / User Profile Section > Status Bar
elements.description: System status bar at the very top of the screen displaying '9:41', wireless signal indicators, and battery status.
elements.explanation: Bounding box covers the full screen instead of just the status bar, which only spans the top. Suggested resize to tightly fit status bar area.

elements.label: Balance Summary > Label
elements.description: Light gray text 'Balance' positioned below the user profile section, acting as a header for the account balance display.
elements.explanation: Original box is far too wide, covering all balance elements. Corrected to tightly fit just the 'Balance' label.

elements.label: Balance Summary > Amount
elements.description: Large bold text '$10 524.15' displayed prominently below the Balance label, showing the current numerical value.
elements.explanation: Box is a bit too wide, including some space to the left and right; suggested coordinates tightly fit the numerical amount.

elements.label: Balance Summary > Add Funds Button
elements.description: Circular dark button with white plus (+) icon positioned to the right of the balance amount.
elements.explanation: Bounding box fits the Add Funds button closely with minimal extra space.

elements.label: Balance Summary > Transfer Button
elements.description: Circular dark button with white transfer arrows icon positioned at the far right of the balance display row.
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely contains the Transfer button; nearly perfect match.
